5. VSCode DevContainer ì„¤ì •
.devcontainer/devcontainer.json
```
{
  "name": "Python & Poetry & TypeScript & NextJS & MySQL",
  "dockerComposeFile": "docker-compose.yml",
  "service": "app",
  "workspaceFolder": "/workspaces/${localWorkspaceFolderBasename}",
